item.minium_me.minium_multitool.desc.1: Extract raw materials for Sea Lantern, Glowstone, and Honeycomb Block
item.minium_me.minium_multitool.desc.3: The same function as right-click of Shovel and Axe
item.minium_me.minium_multitool.desc.4: Trial Spawner cool time reduced to 9/10
block.minium_me.easy_grinder.desc: If Mobs step on it, the Mobs take %.f damage. This causes the killed Mob to lose experience, but not the loot from the player's kill.
block.minium_me.advanced_grinder.desc: If Mobs step on it, the Mobs take %.0f damage. Mob killed by this will drop experience and loot from the player's kill.
block.minium_me.iris_quartz_grinder.desc: If Mobs step on it, the Mobs take %.0f damage. Mob killed by this will drop experience and loot from the player's kill. Looting Lv.X is applied.
block.minium_me.minium_passable_glass.de: Only players or Projectiles summoned by the player can pass through.
item.minium_me.temporally_block_placer.d: Place temporary blocks that will disappear over time. The remain amount will recover over time.
Applying the Durability enchantment causes the temporary block's remaining durability to stop decreasing at a certain probability.
Applying an Efficiency enchantment increases the rate at which remaining charges are restored.
Applying the Fortune enchantment increases the duration before it disappears.
Applying the Silk Touch enchantment prevents it from disappearing.
item.minium_me.deepslate_miner.desc: Capable of destroying deepslate and tuff in a 5x5x5 area in one lump sum. It will be gone after one use.
item.minium_me.wind_exploder.desc: It creates a blast at your feet. If you are gliding, you can fly in the direction you are headed, but be careful not to collide with it.
item.minium_me.advanced_wind_exploder.de: Improved Wind Exploder. Enchantable with Unbreaking and Mending. And shorter cool time.
item.minium_me.wind_exploder.desc.extra: Press the %s key during glide to boost using the blast wave.
item.minium_me.smithing_template.iris_qu: Add Concentrated Minium Armor, Tool, Weapon, Iris Quartz ChestPlate
Add Iris Quartz Ingot(When update Iris Quartz ChestPlate, Add Iris Quartz Elytra)
Concentrated Minium Armor, Tool, Weapon, Iris Quartz ChestPlate
Iris Quartz Ingot(When update Iris Quartz ChestPlate, Iris Quartz Elytra)
item.minium_me.iris_quartz_multitool.des: By Double-right-clicking on a stone-based block while sneaking, you can destroy all stone-based blocks in a 7x7x7 area at once.
item.minium_me.iris_quartz_apple.desc.0: Eating this increases your Max Health by %d.
item.minium_me.iris_quartz_apple.desc.1: Warning! If MaxHealthFix is not loaded, your current HP will be reset!
Gain Poison Heal Effect and Prevent fall damage and collision damage.
When you die, you consume and revive, but a minute cooldown is imposed.
If you fall into the void, in dimensions with a ceiling you will respawn at the spawn point, and in dimensions without a ceiling you will be granted Slow Falling and warped to a high location.
Some effects are enhanced, Reduce damage except for certain parts and Prevent wither damage when wearing a full set of Iris Quartz equipment.
item.minium_me.energy.type.error.desc: There is invalid energy. Use for reset.
item.minium_me.energy.type.empty.desc: There is no energy in it. Hold the gun in your main hand and the ore in your off hand and use it while sneaking to load it.
item.minium_me.energy.type.coal.desc: Fire attribute attack. Note that it cannot damage mobs that are resistant to the fire attribute.
item.minium_me.energy.type.copper.desc: It has the same power as iron, but costs twice as much. If copper energy is used from the block, this block may be weathered or waxed.
item.minium_me.energy.type.gold.desc: It has the effect of making the mobs it hits emit light.
item.minium_me.energy.type.lapis.desc: Random effects are applied to mobs that are hit.
item.minium_me.energy.type.redstone.desc: Slightly shorter cool time and reduce the invincibility time of a hit mob opponent. It also installs energy that emits redstone power at the point of impact.
item.minium_me.energy.type.diamond.desc: More powerful than other ores and gems.It is even more powerful against bosses.
item.minium_me.energy.type.emerald.desc: Note that the attack will go through against mobs that disable flying tools, but will be repelled against Breeze.
item.minium_me.energy.type.quartz.desc: Note that blocks cannot be used as energy.
item.minium_me.energy.type.glowstone.des: It has the effect of making the mobs it hits emit light. When it lands on a block, it leaves a glowstone light.
item.minium_me.energy.type.netherite.des: It is very powerful and can also give Wither effect.
item.minium_me.energy.type.amethyst.desc: Note that blocks cannot be used as energy.
item.minium_me.energy.type.c_minium.desc: It is as powerful as Netherite.
item.minium_me.energy.type.osmium.desc: More powerful than steel. It has the additional effect of poisoning.
item.minium_me.energy.type.iris_quartz.d: It is very powerful but has the worst cost performance.
item.minium_me.energy.type.source_gem.de: When it hits an enemy, it gives a random favorable effect to the player who shot it. Shooting at tame mobs can restore their health.
item.minium_me.energy.type.aluminium.des: Easy to shoot continuously and reduce the invincibility time of a hit mob opponent.
item.minium_me.energy.type.lead.desc: It has the additional effect of poisoning.
item.minium_me.energy.type.tin.desc: Increases damage to mobs touching water.
item.minium_me.energy.type.uranium.desc: Significantly increased damage against Illager, Villager and Player.
item.minium_me.energy.type.zinc.desc: When it stops, satiety is restored for a short period of time with a certain probability.
item.minium_me.energy.type.bronze.desc: It has high firepower and ignores flying tools, but like copper, it is one shot for two ores, so fuel consumption is not good.
item.minium_me.energy.type.steel.desc: It has the effect of setting the target on fire, and while it is burning, the damage increases, but it is not effective against Mobs that are resistant to fire. It is also less powerful against Mobs who are in contact with water.
item.minium_me.energy.type.certus_quartz: Like quartz, Note that blocks cannot be used as energy.
item.minium_me.energy.type.refined_glows: Increased power against Undead. It has the effect of making the mobs it hits emit light. When it lands on a block, it leaves a glowstone light.
item.minium_me.energy.type.refined_obsid: More powerful than Netherite. But can't give Wither effect.
item.minium_me.energy.type.ruby.desc: Increases damage against mobs that disable Freeze damage.
item.minium_me.energy.type.sapphire.desc: Penetrates projectile resistance and increases damage against mobs that can breathe underwater without being undead.
item.minium_me.energy.type.electrum.desc: Slows down Undead and makes everything else glow.
item.minium_me.energy.type.peridot.desc: Its power increases in areas exposed to sunlight.
item.minium_me.energy.type.brass.desc: It costs two to fire one shot and restores health when attacking.
item.minium_me.energy.type.advanced_allo: Power and additional effects are determined randomly.
item.minium_me.energy.type.invar.desc: Increases damage against fire-resistant mobs and inflicts the wither status.
item.minium_me.energy.type.titanium.desc: In addition to damage reduction from armor, it ignores damage reduction-type enchantments.
item.minium_me.energy.type.chrome.desc: Dealing the finishing blow with this attack restores fullness proportional to the opponent's maximum HP.
item.minium_me.energy.type.iridium.desc: It deals high base damage and inflicts additional damage on targets with over half their health remaining.
item.minium_me.energy.type.platinum.desc: High base damage, with an 80% chance to not consume bullets.
item.minium_me.energy.unusable: §7§oThis energy is not available in the current configuration
item.minium_me.iris_quartz_elytra.desc: Press the %s key during glide to boost using the blast wave (cooldown: %f seconds)
item.minium_me.iris_quartz_elytra.desc.u: §7§oBoosting is not possible because the key has not been set.
item.minium_me.iris_quartz_mace.desc.0: When you press and hold the right mouse button and release while touching a block or entity, it creates an explosion centered on that target.
item.minium_me.iris_quartz_mace.desc.1: If the target is an entity, it deals damage and knock them back hard.
death.attack.minium_energy.item: %1$s were bathed in energy by %2$s using %3$s
enchantment.minium_me.stone_alchemy.desc: When you use RangeBreak, stones will no longer drop, but experience and ore will drop occasionally instead.
block.minium_me.stone_alchemy_break_ston: For Stone Alchemy Loot Table - Stone
block.minium_me.stone_alchemy_break_neth: For Stone Alchemy Loot Table - Netherrack
block.minium_me.stone_alchemy_break_end_: For Stone Alchemy Loot Table - End Stone
effect.minium_me.poison_heal.description: It nullifies damage caused by poison and restores strength when poisoned.
effect.minium_me.pickling_salt.descripti: Become damaged when exposed to water.

tag.item.minium_me.iris_quartz_bonus_wea: Weapons that can increase attack power by wearing Iris Quartz equipment all over the body
tag.item.minium_me.minium_equipments: Refining can smelt it into minium nugget.

item.minium_me.armor_reinforced.fire_imm: Equipping one piece of gear, reduces Fire damage by 25%.
Equipping two pieces of gear, reduces Fire damage by 50%.
Equipping three pieces of gear, nullifying Fire damage, it ignites itself when frozen.
Equipping four pieces of gear, healing while burning and maintains vision within lava.
item.minium_me.armor_reinforced.frozen_i: Equipping one piece of gear, reduces Frozen damage by 50%.
Equipping two pieces of gear, frost Walker nullifies damage that can be nullified and nullifies Frozen Damage.
Equipping three pieces of gear, Visibility is maintained in powder snow, preventing burial and allowing movement speed to remain unchanged.
Equipping four pieces of gear, When attacked, it counters with ice-elemental damage and freezes the opponent.
item.minium_me.armor_reinforced.water_ad: Increases the duration of underwater breathing. Increases underwater movement speed even without underwater walking.
Equipping three piece of gear, Gain Conduit Power while in contact with water.
Equipping four pieces of gear, While in contact with water, you gain various bonuses and also deplete the oxygen of any opponents who attack you.
For enemies on the ground, we'll salt them.
item.minium_me.armor_reinforced.all_prot: It can reduce damage, including attacks that ignore all resistances like Void damage.
Equipping one piece of gear, Reduces damage taken by 10%.
Equipping two pieces of gear, Reduces damage taken by 20%.
Equipping three pieces of gear, Reduces damage taken by 30%.
Equipping four pieces of gear, Reduces damage taken by 50% and nullifies all damage for 2 seconds after taking damage.
Adds an effect that revives upon death. However, it cannot be triggered by certain types of damage.
The enhancement effect will be canceled upon activation.
item.minium_me.armor_reinforced.magic_im: Equipping one piece of gear, reduces Magic damage by 25%.
Equipping two pieces of gear, reduces Magic damage by 50%.
Equipping three pieces of gear, nullifies Magic damage
Equipping four pieces of gear, Converts magic damage into healing (capped).
item.minium_me.armor_reinforced.dis_host: You can avoid hostility from some mobs.
Equipping one piece of gear, you will no longer be targeted by the Phantom.
Equipping two pieces of gear, you will no longer be hostile to Piglins even without gold equipment.
Equipping three pieces of gear, you will no longer be targeted by Endermen if you make eye contact with them.
Equipping four pieces of gear, you will no longer be targeted by most mobs unless you attack them first. However, this does not apply to bosses.
item.minium_me.armor_reinforced.wind_amu: Can gain various blessings through the power of the wind.
Equipping one piece of gear, Prevent fall damage and collision damage.
Equipping two pieces of gear, Nullifies damage from projectile attacks. Equipping three pieces of gear, nullifies attacks that aren't ranged weapons and can even reflect them.
Equipping three pieces of gear, When hit while Wind Charged state, it will reduce most attacks by 70% once and cancel Wind Charged state.
Equipping four pieces of gear, Attacking has a certain chance to grant Wind Charged state to yourself.
item.minium_me.tool_reinforced.speed_min: Mining Speed and Movement Speed increase.
item.minium_me.tool_reinforced.wind_slin: Attacking puts you in Wind Charged state in random.
While in Wind Charged state, right-clicking consumes one durability point to fire a Wind Charge.
However, if you have a shield equipped in your off-hand, sneaking is required.
Right-clicking during glide activates Wind Charge, allowing you to boost with an explosive blast.
When holding it in your main hand while in Wind Charged state, it nullifies fall damage.
item.minium_me.tool_reinforced.life_stea: When attacking, absorbs the opponent's Health.
item.minium_me.tool_reinforced.generate_: Consume 5 Durability to place a light source.
item.minium_me.tool_reinforced.honey_pai: Consuming 10 durability points allows you to wax the block.
This ability does not activate while sneaking or when holding a shield in your off-hand.
commands.minium_me.resethealthboost.fail: This has no effect on the target entity.
